videos.headline: FSU's Samuel comes up with early INT
videos.description: Georgia Tech QB Jeff SIms throws downfield, but gets picked off by Florida State DB Asante Samuel Jr.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (FSU's Samuel comes up with early INT) 2020/09/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Blackman finds Helton for FSU TD
videos.description: Florida State QB James Blackman connects with Keyshawn Helton for a three-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Blackman finds Helton for FSU TD) 2020/09/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: FSU's Robinson comes through to block FG
videos.description: Florida State DE Janarius Robinson bursts through the line to block Georgia Tech's field-goal attempt.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (FSU's Robinson comes through to block FG) 2020/09/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Samuel nabs another INT for the Seminoles
videos.description: FSU's Asante Samuel Jr. comes up with his second interception of the game and returns it 36 yards.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Samuel nabs another INT for the Seminoles) 2020/09/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wilson tallies another FG block for FSU
videos.description: FSU's Marvin Wilson jumps high to block Georgia Tech's field-goal attempt, the team's second block of the half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wilson tallies another FG block for FSU) 2020/09/12 ESHEET
